you with a certificate of appreciation from the National Press Club,
and I'd also like to present you with a Press Club paperweight. The
_ my last question _ and I must say that you've taken the wind out
of my sails a little bit. I know that upon retirement you had said
before that you'd like to be a linebacker coach for Tom Landry.
